Welcome !

Kaleidofoundry is a java / jee extensible framework, based on jdk 6 and jee 5 / 6 APIs. It is a technical base for handling : configuration, caching, file resource store, i18n labels & exception messages, jndi resource, mail, messaging... It has been designed to be easily integrated to your current java stack & environment (could be clustered or not, with replicated or distributed caching).
